            <p>
                This project covers real-world S3 architecture patterns:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Use <strong>CloudFront</strong> in production for HTTPS and global CDN caching.</li>
                <li>Enable <strong>S3 encryption</strong> (SSE-S3 or SSE-KMS) for sensitive data.</li>
                <li>Apply <strong>least-privilege bucket policies</strong> - avoid Principal: "*" when possible.</li>
                <li>Use <strong>S3 Intelligent-Tiering</strong> for unpredictable access patterns.</li>
                <li>Monitor <strong>replication metrics</strong> to ensure CRR is working.</li>
